  <front>
    <title>Bidirectional RSVP-TE Tunnel</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-xu-l3vpn-rsvp-te-bidirection-01"/>
    <author initials="X." surname="Xu" fullname="Xiaohu Xu">
      <organization>HUAWEI</organization>
    </author>
    <author initials="L." surname="Zhang" fullname="Le Zhang">
      <organization>HUAWEI</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="19" month="October" year="2005"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   Through the binding of two unidirectional RSVP-TE tunnels established 
   between a pair of LSRs destined to each other, a bidirectional RSVP-
   TE tunnel is formed. The bidirectional RSVP-TE tunnel can be used to 
   establish L3VPN with virtual router technology.  
	 </t>
    </abstract>
